INSTALL
-------

1) Clone this repository.
2) Go to the root folder of this repository on your harddrive.
3) Copy the ./iamsoft/ambiente.default.py to ./iamsoft/ambiente.py and edit it to set your configuration.
4) execute: $ sudo ./install.sh
5) Create the SSL certificate (files iamsoft.pem and iamsoft.key) under /etc/apache2/ssl
6) Create the apache2 configuration files for http and https
7) Verify that the file /etc/apache2/ports.conf has the corresponding ports open.
8) Restart apache2 service.

CREATE ONE AGENCY
1) Enter to iamsoft site.
2) Create an account.
3) Create an agency.
4) execute: $ ./manage.py crear_agencias_pendientes
